ufacturing, Mining, Automotive, Environmental Health, Education and Automation. The company has made expeditious progress into the Singaporean Security Industry, deploying multiple technology products to enhance security workflows, digitalization of data with an alert based real-time monitoring system. Our products have solved the complexity of manual people entry logs and monitoring visitor behavior on any closed community during a restricted time. We further offer Autonomous Mobile Robots for various applications like serving food in restaurants, patrolling, and cargo transfer. ', 'employee_count': 49, 'employee_range': '51-200', 'follower_count': 6375, 'hq_full_address': 'F No.348-1A3, Sri Lakshmi Nagar II,  Thanneer Pandhal Road, Peelamedu, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641004, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/katomaran', 'public_id': 'katomaran'}, {'company_id': '13265431', 'company_name': 'Montbleu Technologies Private Limited', 'description': 'We provide superior quality solutions, keeping the focus on helping our customers reach their business goals.\nAs a full-service technology services company, we offer consulting services, Digital Enterprise Solutions, and Product Engineering Solutions. ', 'employee_count': 118, 'employee_range': '51-200', 'follower_count': 5616, 'hq_full_address': '2000, Krishna Colony, , Trichy Road, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641005, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/montbleu-technologies-pvt-ltd', 'public_id': 'montbleu-technologies-pvt-ltd'}, {'company_id': '82995959', 'company_name': 'Gravity AI', 'description': '', 'employee_count': 3, 'employee_range': '0-1', 'follower_count': 4405, 'hq_full_address': 'KCT Tech Park, Saravanampatti-Thudiyalur Road, Saravanampatti, Forge Incubation Center, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641035, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thegravityai', 'public_id': 'thegravityai'}, {'company_id': '89502982', 'company_name': 'VictorFlow', 'description': "We're VictorFlow Agency, With over decade of experience in the digital business field as a Researchers, Developers, Designers & Illustrators.\n\nWe’ve created more number of well-crafted Websites, Graphics Designs, Illustrations by connecting business goals with customers needs. We're very focused on getting a perfect proposition from the customers what they and their business actually need.", 'employee_count': 3, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 2488, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 642001, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/victorflow', 'public_id': 'victorflow'}, {'company_id': '82830481', 'company_name': 'QUICKFRESHES', 'description': "We're a team of creative, driven and persistent people. We want to revolutionize your nearest local shop to an quick commerce online store in our app.\n\nWelcome to Quick Freshes. We are a quick commerce app,that allows you to get delivery of products quickly under 10 to 20 minutes as customers value their nearest shops so we have come up with a simple way to get your products quickly delivered from your nearest shops Through our app only If your nearest shops are available in our application and we will be covering most of the shops around tier 1 and tier 2 cities across India.\n\nWe want to re-imagine the ideal way of life in future to save time and effort of people to order essentials,goods & Commodities.", 'employee_count': 0, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 2287, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/quickfreshes', 'public_id': 'quickfreshes'}, {'company_id': '31555535', 'company_name': 'ERPROOTS Private Limited', 'description': "Our single-minded focus to be the world's best SAP logistics consulting company, enabled us to amplify the business results of our partners. Started in the year 2017, ERPROOTS has over 300+ man-years of collective SAP  experience. With a focus in developing and delivering SAP Logistics and SCM solutions, we have served clients across Europe (Belgium, Germany, Austria), USA, UK & in the Middle East.\n\nERPROOTS has developed multiple template-based and standalone developments that cater to the SAP Logistics and Supply Chain Management specific modules that can be implemented and integrated with existing solutions in a fast track manner, not compromising the business requirement whilst ensuring quicker ROI.", 'employee_count': 134, 'employee_range': '51-200', 'follower_count': 2192, 'hq_full_address': '4th Floor, N Towers, 25, Tex Park Road,,  Nehru Nagar West, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641014, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/erproots', 'public_id': 'erproots'}, {'company_id': '26663030', 'company_name': 'AlienX', 'description': 'Startup company which brings the young brain to discover more and more innovations to the world."The significant problems we face cannot be solved by the same level of thinking that created them."', 'employee_count': 2, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 2050, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641654, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/alienxtech', 'public_id': 'alienxtech'}, {'company_id': '13272660', 'company_name': 'GDG Coimbatore', 'description': "GDG Coimbatore is a Coimbatore-based non-profit developers group to learn, share and know more about technologies. The industry is growing like never before, and we're trying to push the community forward to keep up with the industry. We are constantly trying to push ourselves to bring the best of technology to you through sessions and unlimited resources. And this is just the beginning.", 'employee_count': 10, 'employee_range': '201-500', 'follower_count': 1782, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641029, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/gdgcoimbatore', 'public_id': 'gdgcoimbatore'}, {'company_id': '13278704', 'company_name': 'Datinfi Private Limited', 'description': 'Datinfi was founded in Coimbatore, Tamilnadu, India, in 2016 by analysts and machine learning experts to bring the power of transformative technology to core business operations of SMEs.\n\nWith the unique combination of information gathering and analysis, we build algorithms that iteratively learn from data and deliver hidden insights. While the concept of machine learning isn’t new, its ability to apply complex mathematical calculations to automatically extract useful information is a recent development.\n\nSome of its latest applications that you might be familiar with:\n\nWeb searches that recognize inputs, display relevant searches, predict results on relevance and return a ranked output.\nTracking of social media to know what people are saying about your brand/business/services.\nExtracting actionable insights from redundant data.\n\nDatinfi offers a range of services including:\n1. Data as a Service\n2. Brand Monitoring Services \n3. Data Visualization Service\n4. Data Quality Assurance \n5. Data Advisory Services', 'employee_count': 28, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 1769, 'hq_full_address': '75-77 Blossom Enclave, 1st Floor, Tatabad, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641012, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/datainfi', 'public_id': 'datainfi'}, {'company_id': '79541417', 'company_name': 'Hirezo.co', 'description': "Hirezo.co is a Talent Solutions & Full Stack Recruitment Company sourcing candidate's for Top companies from all sectors in India & Overseas Countries.\n\nBuild your career with us.\n\nFor business related queries mail us at : info@hirezo.co", 'employee_count': 3, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 1728, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641006, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/hirezo-co', 'public_id': 'hirezo-co'}, {'company_id': '80211158', 'company_name': 'Exterro India', 'description': 'Exterro®, Inc. is the leading provider of e-discovery and information governance software specifically designed for in-house legal, privacy and IT teams at Global 2000 and Am Law 200 organizations. Built on a simple concept of process optimization, Exterro helps organizations address their regulatory, compliance, and litigation risks more effectively and at lower costs. Exterro is the exclusive ACC Alliance partner for e-discovery software.\n', 'employee_count': 38, 'employee_range': '201-500', 'follower_count': 1673, 'hq_full_address': 'Tidel Park, Module No. 104, First Floor, Villankurichi Rd, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641014, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/exterro-india', 'public_id': 'exterro-india'}, {'company_id': '13217573', 'company_name': 'Walinns Innovation', 'description': 'Walinns is a Mobile App Marketing and Analytics platform offering app marketers to measure and analyze user engagement and tools to retain users through powerful marketing tools. \n\nFounder & CEO - Ram Viswanathan \n\nSign up for free trial - https://app.walinns.com/signup', 'employee_count': 44, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 1401, 'hq_full_address': 'Tidel Park , Elcot SEZ, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641014, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/walinns-innovation', 'public_id': 'walinns-innovation'}, {'company_id': '64795683', 'company_name': 'Future Forward Technologies (FFT)', 'description': "I see that you are checking out my page for a reason - you must be facing some challenges. Well, I'm here to provide you with solutions.\n\nWhat are the issues you're dealing with?\n\nWeb Design | Web Apps | Web Development\nMobile Apps | Android | iOS\nEnterprise Software | Custom Software\nE-Commerce | Woo-Commerce\nFront-End | User Experience\nBranding | Logos\nSEO | Digital Marketing | Content Writing\n\nDo you need a solution for any of the problems listed above? We believe that providing solutions is more important than the technical aspect.\n\nNone of these issues apply to you?\n\nWe also offer additional services, such as the option to hire.\n \nContract or Part-Time\n\ndevelopers who can develop better solutions for any of your problems.\n\nStill not interested?\n\nWe also have a variety of ready-made software products for \n\nWeb and Mobile Apps\n\navailable for purchase. If you're interested in buying any of these products, please let me know.\n\nIf you don't require any of our services, that's okay. You're always welcome to visit my page.\n\nThank you for being here.\n\nBest regards,\n\nFuture Forward Technologies - FFT\nwww.fftech.in", 'employee_count': 3, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 1392, 'hq_full_address': '79/5 Vanjima nagar, Palamalai Road, Periyanaickenpalayam, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641020, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/fftech', 'public_id': 'fftech'}, {'company_id': '28729224', 'company_name': 'Vendora - Supplier Relationship Management & Procure-to-pay Software', 'description': 'Many organizations have a problem to engage with their vendors at every step. Especially when it comes to dealing with multiple vendors, it’s must to adopt Vendor Management tools that empowers you to deploy a structured Vendor on-boarding program and keep them self-sufficient.\n\nWith Vendor Management Software solution in place you could maintain a positive relationship, catch potential problems before they arise. Besides, be fully aware of, whether your vendors are aligned to set benchmark or target and see to if any course correction action needs to be taken from both sides to achieve common business goals.', 'employee_count': 1, 'employee_range': '51-200', 'follower_count': 1279, 'hq_full_address': '1247 Trichy Road, Jupiter House, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641045, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/vendora-scm-software', 'public_id': 'vendora-scm-software'}, {'company_id': '13575114', 'company_name': 'Vtail Commerce Private Limited', 'description': 'Vtail Commerce is a Global Trading Company founded in January 2017. ', 'employee_count': 17, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 1170, 'hq_full_address': '63/2, Alvin Nagar, Sungam Bypass, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu  641045, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/vtailcommerce', 'public_id': 'vtailcommerce'}, {'company_id': '72381630', 'company_name': 'Innovation Geeks ', 'description': 'Innovation Geeks is a forward-looking company focused on building products and solutions. We convert your ideas into reality. ', 'employee_count': 6, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 1085, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/innovation-geeks-private-ltd', 'public_id': 'innovation-geeks-private-ltd'}, {'company_id': '10630072', 'company_name': 'Produle', 'description': 'Produle is a high tech software product company specializing in UI design tools. We make "MockFlow"\u200b a UI planning platform for designers that provides an end-to-end solution for product design.\n\nWe are proudly nerdy and passionate about our craft. People do their greatest work when they are inspired. That\'s why we\'ve taken care to design beautiful work environments that motivate and energize amazing people. We take on tough challenges and solve problems that not everyone gets to tackle in their careers.\n\nTo learn more, visit\nMockFlow Website: https://mockflow.com\nCompany Website: http://produle.com\n', 'employee_count': 12, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count'