e authorized users will have access to login and view data on a web-based cloud platform integrated with digital maps.\n\nTrinetra iWay cloud platform has features like Dashboard, Schedule Management, Monitor, History, Landmarks, Alarms & more. Intelligent reports are available for analysis and decision making, which can be exported to pdf, word or excel.', 'employee_count': 1, 'employee_range': '51-200', 'follower_count': 669, 'hq_full_address': '#1247, Trichy Road, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641045, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/trinetra-iway', 'public_id': 'trinetra-iway'}, {'company_id': '71828951', 'company_name': 'Ingenious Tech', 'description': 'a purpose driven organization in the pursuit of perpetual progress through innovation and technology with continual learning and contextual knowledge', 'employee_count': 1, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 653, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ingenioustech', 'public_id': 'ingenioustech'}, {'company_id': '3758824', 'company_name': 'LogBase', 'description': 'Industry-leading eCommerce solutions for Shopify Merchants.\nServing 25,000+ Shopify stores globally.', 'employee_count': 27, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 648, 'hq_full_address': 'PSG STEP, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641045, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/logbase-inc-', 'public_id': 'logbase-inc-'}, {'company_id': '80789799', 'company_name': 'Hidden Beyond (Yellow Whale Labs Pvt Ltd)', 'description': 'Game and DApp development company that focuses on building next-gen blockchain products. ', 'employee_count': 10, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 645, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/yellowwhale', 'public_id': 'yellowwhale'}, {'company_id': '27500515', 'company_name': 'Vettrix', 'description': "At Vettrix CRM, we're passionate about helping our customers achieve their business goals through innovative technology solutions. As a trusted partner in digital transformation, we offer a range of services that enable our customers to stay ahead of the competition.\n\nOur team of experienced consultants specializes in SAP, offering end-to-end services from implementation to support. We're committed to providing our customers with the expertise they need to succeed in today's fast-paced business environment.\n\nIn addition to our SAP services, we also offer a powerful CRM solution that helps businesses of all sizes optimize their sales processes and drive growth. \nOur CRM is designed to be user-friendly, customizable, and scalable to meet the unique needs of each of our customers.\n\nWe believe in building long-term relationships with our customers. We work closely with each of our clients to understand their business needs and develop solutions that deliver measurable results. \n\nIf you're looking for a partner to help you achieve your business goals, look no further than Vettrix CRM.\n\nThis company is based out of JKR Tower, 5/4 Moonlight Garden,SITRA Road, Kalapatti, Coimbatore-641048, Tamil Nadu, India.", 'employee_count': 18, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 620, 'hq_full_address': 'JKR Tower, 5/4 Moonlight Garden, SITRA Road, Kalapatti, COIMBATORE, Tamil Nadu 641048, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/vettrix', 'public_id': 'vettrix'}, {'company_id': '3477356', 'company_name': 'EP Software Technologies Pvt Ltd', 'description': 'EP Technologies is a diverse end-to-end IT solutions provider. It offers a range of expertise that are aimed at helping customers re-engineer and re-invent their businesses to compete successfully in an ever-changing marketplace. EP Technologies has presence in two countries and a customer base spanning from Fortune 500 companies to major staffing vendors. \r\n\r\nBy leveraging our expertise, customers are able to focus on their core business activities. It liberates them from routine operational activities like designing and implementing information systems. As an organization with methodologies, EP Technologies also ensures a high level of client comfort through reliable Service Level Agreements.\r\n\r\nWe continue to reiterate our key imperatives of focusing on our technology competencies and keeping pace with continuous growth and learning. We believe that in technology there are no half-measures. Our growth has come as a result of our unique business model and clearly defined growth strategies. Offshore-led, technology-centric, powered by domain expertise when we talk about delivering value at EP Tech, we back it with a proven track record of reduced costs, quicker time-to-market and greatly increased productivity.', 'employee_count': 47, 'employee_range': '201-500', 'follower_count': 614, 'hq_full_address': 'Sree Kumaran Salai, Avinashi Road, Aerodrome Post, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641 014, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ep-software-technologies', 'public_id': 'ep-software-technologies'}, {'company_id': '2450791', 'company_name': 'PM Square Soft Services Pvt Ltd - Custom Software Development Company', 'description': "Hello! We are PM Square Soft Services Private Limited, your go-to IT solutions provider based in Coimbatore, India. Our team of experts specializes in critical communication device integration, advanced facial recognition systems, GPS tracking systems, pipe fabrication workflow management, and flight schedules. We understand that each client's needs are unique, and that's what drives us to offer a range of services including software development, custom applications, IT consulting, ERP systems, support, and maintenance.\n\nCurrently, we're excited to be working on some groundbreaking projects. We're developing a GUI for critical communication devices and harnessing the power of 5G and Wi-Fi6 to enable seamless communication over Consort’s devices. We're also thrilled about our in-house project - an AI-powered facial recognition system with applications in customer identification, attendance management, and behavior analysis. We believe this technology will revolutionize several sectors and we're eager to be part of that change.\n\nLooking back, we're proud of the relationships we've built and the projects we've executed. We've provided Tetra services across India to Consort Digital Private Limited and offered our expertise to Suguna Foods Limited, an international brand. We've crafted GPS-based asset protection devices for our US client and built a comprehensive flight planning system for an aviation client. Our collaboration with AZCO Inc resulted in a robust pipe fabrication workflow system.\n\nWe take pride in our contributions to public safety too. We've implemented tetra-tracking solutions for Police Departments in Salem and Tirunelveli. Plus, we're behind Vazhikaatti, a popular GPS Tracking portal.\n\nWhile we're proud of our past, we're even more excited about our future. We look forward to continuing to serve our clients, push boundaries, and drive innovation in the IT industry.", 'employee_count': 8, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 603, 'hq_full_address': '3, Shree, 5th Cross Rd, Venkatesam, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu  641041, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pmsquaresoft', 'public_id': 'pmsquaresoft'}, {'company_id': '78407656', 'company_name': 'Zeoner India Pvt Ltd', 'description': 'Zeoner founded in the year 2018, is a Health IT platform that focuses on minimizing the cost of healthcare technology globally to empower people to live their life to the fullest.', 'employee_count': 18, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 600, 'hq_full_address': '29-4 