and manage fashion.", 'employee_count': 21, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 463, 'hq_full_address': 'Office No: 2, 8th Floor, Mayflower Valencia, Avinashi Rd, Udayampalayam, NavaIndia , Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641004, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ad-hash-technolabs-pvt-ltd', 'public_id': 'ad-hash-technolabs-pvt-ltd'}, {'company_id': '97213103', 'company_name': 'Transgenie', 'description': "Transgenie proudly serves as the premier delivery management software partner for over 50 global businesses, specializing in innovative solutions such as Product Traceability Software for various Industries, On-demand Delivery Platform, Last-Mile Delivery Software, and Q-commerce Solutions. In the fast-paced realm of digital evolution, TransGenie stands as a beacon, committed to delivering superior supply chain solutions. Our focus is on curating platforms that not only simplify but also seamlessly integrate all aspects of business operations into a unified, efficient system.\n\nAt TransGenie, we embrace the transformative power of technology to deliver unparalleled efficiency in supply chain management. Our commitment is to serve as your trusted partner in navigating the complexities of modern business logistics.\n\nLet's forge a connection and jointly explore the possibilities of reshaping the future of supply chain dynamics. With a handshake of collaboration and a sparkle of innovation, TransGenie invites you to visit www.transgenie.com to embark on a transformative journey today.", 'employee_count': 2, 'employee_range': '51-200', 'follower_count': 440, 'hq_full_address': '2 CM Nagar, Ramakrishnapuram, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641006, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/transgenie', 'public_id': 'transgenie'}, {'company_id': '14406192', 'company_name': 'Laravel Ecommerce Shopping Cart Software', 'description': 'No matter what size of your business, we o