ems India (P) Limited.', 'description': 'Zettastack Systems is a Software Development Company that focuses on highly qualitative, timely delivered, and cost-effective technology solutions. We ensure quality standards are matched while developing software solutions that give your business an edge over competitors. Our global software delivery model ensures we deliver maximum targeted results to YOU. We build developing products and applications which match global standards. We aspire to have our global presence with offices in USA and Development Center in India. We believe to deliver quality, love to accomplish our tasks & always passionate about technology. We build applications that add value to our clients and contribute to their growth.', 'employee_count': 9, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 405, 'hq_full_address': 'Ground Floor 13, Ground Floor 14, Tidel Park, SEZ, Vilankuruchi Road, Coimbatore, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641005, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/zettastack', 'public_id': 'zettastack'}, {'company_id': '3240090', 'company_name': 'flowturb Solutions', 'description': 'Flowturb Solutions is known for its impeccable service and provides assistance to industries in understanding this complex behavior of fluids using state of the art research tools like Computational Fluid Dynamics.\r\n   The name Flowturb Solutions was inspired by one of the most complex and fascinating physical phenomenon, fluid turbulence. Fluid plays an important part in our everyday endeavours more than we have ever realized. We have adapted over selves so well to our environment that we do not realize, we are living in an ocean of air. From complex super sonic flows over space crafts to simple flow inside a conduit, fluid plays an vital part in every field of engineering. To understand fluid behaviour would be the key in understanding any mechanism/system that is related to it.', 'employee_count': 5, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 395, 'hq_full_address': '1467, Sathy Road,, Ramakrishnapuram,, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641006, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/flowtursolutions', 'public_id': 'flowtursolutions'}, {'company_id': '95732494', 'company_name': 'Teeming Infotech', 'description': "Teeming Infotech: Unlocking the Power of Psychographic Design, Persuasive Technology, Neuro Marketing Strategy, and Cognitive Business Solutions\n\nWelcome to Teeming Infotech, a cutting-edge technology firm at the forefront of revolutionizing the way businesses connect with their customers. With a deep understanding of human psychology and advanced technological expertise, we offer a range of transformative services including psychographic design, persuasive technology, neuro marketing strategy, and cognitive business solutions.\n\nIn today's competitive landscape, it is crucial for businesses to truly understand their target audience at a deeper level. That's where our psychographic design services come into play. By delving beyond demographics and exploring the intricate nuances of consumer behavior, attitudes, values, and motivations, we help businesses create tailored experiences that resonate with their customers on a profound level. Our team of skilled professionals utilizes a combination of research, data analysis, and design principles to craft engaging and personalized interactions that drive customer loyalty and brand advocacy.\n\nLeveraging the power of persuasive technology, we empower businesses to influence customer behavior in a positive and meaningful way. By seamlessly integrating principles of behavioral psychology and technology, we create compelling digital experiences that nudge users towards desired actions. From intuitive user interfaces to persuasive content and interactive features, our persuasive technology solutions are designed to captivate users' attention, drive engagement, and maximize conversions.\n\nNeuro marketing strategy is another area where Teeming Infotech excels. By drawing insights from neuroscience and cognitive psychology, we help businesses understand how the human brain responds to marketing stimuli. Armed with this knowledge, we develop neuroscience-driven strategies that tap into consumers' emotions, decision-making processes,", 'employee_count': 1, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 395, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/teeming-infotech', 'public_id': 'teeming-infotech'}, {'company_id': '89983735', 'company_name': 'Sapientflux Technologies', 'description': "At Sapientflux Technologies, we are a team of dedicated, skilled, and ambitious technology professionals. We have a proven track record of designing, developing, and maintaining robust IT software systems that meet the specific needs of our parent company, Schnell Energy Equipments Pvt Ltd. This includes management information systems and content management systems that support daily operations, as well as software for IoT projects such as smart city lighting, home security, and remote equipment monitoring.\n\nAs we've grown, we've also taken on the challenge of designing and developing our own products, as well as those for our customers. Our solutions are well-regarded and widely adopted by a diverse range of audiences.\n\nOur research capabilities allow us to quickly adopt new and emerging technologies, and we have a philosophy of embracing new developments as they arise. This spirit of innovation is supported by our strong focus on process, which enables us to deliver high-quality products at a rapid pace.\nWe strive to bring technology to the forefront of our clients business by providing them with tailored solutions to their specific needs.", 'employee_count': 2, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 391, 'hq_full_address': 'D & E, Forge Factory, KCT Tech Park, 