ed many people across different streams from Software Developers to Architects, Managers to core Leadership members. Now we have embarked on the path to impart the knowledge and experience to the organizations that intend to build great teams and products.', 'employee_count': 2, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 339, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641041, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/teamnexus', 'public_id': 'teamnexus'}, {'company_id': '90688444', 'company_name': 'Reviuo.com', 'description': ' Our platform provides comprehensive reviews and recommendations for a wide range of software products, with a focus on delivering personalized recommendations to each user. ', 'employee_count': 0, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 324, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/reviuo', 'public_id': 'reviuo'}, {'company_id': '82100937', 'company_name': 'Cyber Reach', 'description': 'Cyber Reach | Cyber Security | Amrita Vishwa Vidyapeetham', 'employee_count': 0, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 310, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641112, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/cyber-reach/', 'public_id': 'https:www.linkedin.comshowcasecyber-reach'}, {'company_id': '18654112', 'company_name': 'Lumhaa: The Memory Jar Company', 'description': 'Keep everything important safe with memory jars 🙌\n\n🆓 FREE, UNLIMITED STORAGE\nAdd all photos, videos, audio, notes, documents, and text messages that matter to you in your private memory jars\n\n👪 FOR ALL THE PEOPLE YOU CARE ABOUT\nCreate as many memory jars as you want for your different groups. Only people you invite inside each memory jar can see what is inside it (not even us). You can even make jars just for yourself to save memories, no inviting required :)\n\n👀 DIFFERENT VIEWS\nView your memories as slideshows, calendars, maps, and more\n\n🏺 GET PHYSICAL PRODUCTS\nOrder physical versions of your jars and memories. The perfect gift!\n\n🚫 NO ADS, EVER\nWe do not share your data or have any ads. Instead, we monetize through physical products and subscriptions from organizations. Tell your school/college about us or buy a physical product if you want to support us!\n\n***\n\nPopular memory jars include virtual birthday cards 🎁, baby books 👶, wedding albums 💑, school portfolios 👩\u200d🎓, relationship time capsules 👭🏽, and personal diaries 📓\n\nMade with ❤️ using award winning psychology research on happiness and psychological well being. For questions, contact +91 80984 93568 or info@lumhaa.com', 'employee_count': 7, 'employee_range': '2-10', 'follower_count': 309, 'hq_full_address': '126G Renaissance Terrace, TS Road, Race Course , Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641018, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/lumhaa', 'public_id': 'lumhaa'}, {'company_id': '3795037', 'company_name': 'TaxiMobility', 'description': 'TaxiMobility provides an end-to-end dispatching solution to cabbies. This makes ease of booking and allocate jobs to driver with effortless. Its a huge revolution in taxi business that expands capability of managing cab dispatch needs through technology.', 'employee_count': 2, 'employee_range': '201-500', 'follower_count': 300, 'hq_full_address': 'Module No. 405 4th Floor, North Block, Elcot SEZ, Tidel Park, B.R., Coimbatore IT Park Rd, B.R. Puram Industrial Estate, Peelamedu,, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641 041, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/taximobility', 'public_id': 'taximobility'}, {'company_id': '14610125', 'company_name': 'byteFACTORY', 'description': 'A SaaS based Intelligent Product Lifecycle Management System through effective digital technologies such as Industrial Internet of Things and Artificial Intelligence. byteFACT