uke Technologies is a small digital design studio inspired by people who are changing the world. We focus on solving problems to produce intelligent designs, deliver engaging experiences and build meaningful connections. We work with great clients all over the world to create thoughtful and purposeful products.\n\nWe specialize in great service, exceptional design and engaging interactive experiences for humans.\n\nAbove all, we believe in quality design, attention to detail, interaction, experimentation, collaboration, exploration and everything digital.', 'employee_count': 1, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 212, 'hq_full_address': 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641030, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/smartduke-technologies', 'public_id': 'smartduke-technologies'}, {'company_id': '78725372', 'company_name': 'Coding Club GCT', 'description': 'Programming powers the digital world. We all could unarguably agree on the fact that coding has become more than being important in day-to-day life. It has become a necessity. Every website, smartphone app, computer program, calculator, and even microwave relies on code in order to operate.\n\nTo empower the GCT student community with the coding skills and to expose them to the ocean of opportunities available, the Coding Club has been formed.\n\nHere we practice and participate in programming competitions, solving real-world problems\nDevelop applications, provide tech support to our college, and work on open source contributions.', 'employee_count': 6, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 204, 'hq_full_address': 'Thadagam road, G.C.T. post., Near to Agricultural university, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641013, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/coding-club-gct', 'public_id': 'coding-club-gct'}, {'company_id': '86183410', 'company_name': 'Thirvu Soft Private Limited', 'description': 'Thirvu Soft Private Li