ty applications for limousine and taxi companies. We have completed several successful and operating models. Contact us for details.\n\n\nWe are a full cycle app development company. We specialize in native iOS and Android apps. Here is a list of our services:\n•\tDesktop Apps\n•\tMobile Apps\n•\tWeb Apps\n•\tUX/UI designs\n•\tOutsourced Programming\n•\tCloud Services\n•\tData Science AI\n•\tSoftware Consulting\n•\tAPIs\n•\tIoT\n\n\nWe use agile / waterfall methodology depending on our client’s requirement. We pride ourselves in the transparency of our processes. Our clients are involved and in control of every stage of the development process. We pay special attention in our designs to the interfaces and user experience, in addition we also set the analytics and create all needed reports for business owners. \nOur aftersales department ensure you receive all the needed support during the deployment face & after going live.\n\n\nInterested to join us? Indipro Technologies is currently hiring for the following positions:\n\nDevelopment Team:\n•\tProject Manager\n•\tAndroid Developer\n•\tPEGA Developer\n\n \nBusiness Team:\n•\tSoftware Sales engineer - for the Middle East and Europe\n•\tTechnical Content Writer – for web content, software development, \n•\tContent Creator - for the innovative social media content\n•\tUX Designer\n•\tUI designer\n\n\nWe have a result oriented culture with hybrid / remote working model available.\n\nPlease send your CV to jobs@indiprotechnologies.com\n\n\nOur offices:\n•\tIndia - Coimbatore\n•\tLebanon – Beirut\n•\tBelgium - Brussels\n\n\nOur CLUTCH profile:\nOur Nasscom profile:\n\nOur social media: \nYoutube | Facebook | Instagram @indiprotechnologies', 'employee_count': 3, 'employee_range': '11-50', 'follower_count': 142, 'hq_full_address': 'Saraswathi Enclave, Vellingiri Nagar, Navavoor Pirivu, Vadavalli , No 32, 1st Floor, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641041, IN', 'industry': 'Software Development', 'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.