2025-08-14 09:28:14,109 | INFO  | LinkedinProvider.py:40 | {'data': [{'attributes': [], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQHdpT3kJHLJvg/feedshare-shrink_160/B56ZiitGltG4Ag-/0/1755076393066?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=ZsYxs107gwI4MRX7qx-UsiUPC_LOwivyx5kqrcIepYY'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQHc5hzeQ3K1yw/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56ZiitGlpHkAo-/0/1755076392600?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=oA_eD4MzYOxirHi-zkDKO5OiL71oSGlcl4vvbHYdBaA'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGv5MGj0VNveA/feedshare-shrink_1280/B56ZiitGmZG0Ak-/0/1755076393190?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=1L2tEnfNoaFGrpuPLELbjJqwEaW1uslJ_aNNw03y__4'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQG1gHn9XojlOg/feedshare-shrink_1280/B56ZiitGlOG4Ao-/0/1755076392721?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=me5yk6yajChTx-oc9U5LTjvWDg6Hq4hPybJljrg99W0'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_likes': 79, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-08-13 10:30:01', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Our second Manager Mastery session, ‘Let’s Talk Leadership’, was more conversations.\n\nOur People Managers and Team Leads came together to discuss the challenges they face, share experiences, explore new leadership approaches within their teams, and reflect on what leadership looks like in action.\n\nIt was a space to connect, share, and learn from one another.\n\n#GrowingLeaders #Kovaico #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '17 hours ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_growingleaders-kovaico-togetherwegrow-activity-7361343265964519424-bWP_', 'urn': '7361343265964519424'}, {'attributes': [{'first': 'Halima', 'headline': 'Deputy High Commissioner at Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office', 'last': 'Holland', 'public_id': 'halima-holland-1769b3338', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAFTdfCoBCxAudmRejLkPg5lGBkS6DSSzCU8'}, {'first': 'Dr. Sundheep', 'headline': 'Department for International Trade', 'last': 'Balu', 'public_id': 'sundheep', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAAA-9NwB-vULE4UYENWZFQep624uiguQWLs'}, {'first': 'Swetha', 'headline': 'Inward Investment Adviser- Department of Business and Trade', 'last': 'Ratnasabhapathi', 'public_id': 'swetha-ratnasabhapathi', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAACgH4ScB7HtDlKd2bchas_3OT5gywYkCzUk'}, {'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQHq6CdYBWHaBg/feedshare-shrink_160/B56Zidx_OLH0Ac-/0/1754993785641?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=3cDMaIJ5Dwx0ZDbMhXaqgJjhHq4aRGXEaC8XT4CyBJo'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFhroK6RHlCCw/feedshare-shrink_20/B56Zidx_ONHQAw-/0/1754993787167?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=mrSD1cc9xAsMuffGMr-8IDiL4ekSsuJIpnIRlWh5Bio'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFzUK692YpoFA/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56Zidx_OOHkAw-/0/1754993786089?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=9zxZls23lVXTIglr6D-Pr0MhnZ2ipqxCTy6XcSEfFRQ'}], 'num_comments': 1, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 257, 'num_praises': 1, 'num_reposts': 4, 'posted': '2025-08-12 11:00:16', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'We had the pleasure of hosting Ms. Halima Holland, British Deputy High Commissioner, Chennai, along with Dr. Sundheep Balu and Ms. Swetha Ratnasabhapathi, at our Kovai.co #Coimbatore office.\n\xa0\nWe shared our journey, showcased the innovation behind our SaaS products, and discussed how our Coimbatore and London teams collaborate to serve customers worldwide.\n\xa0\nMs. Halima and her team listened to our ideas on how businesses like ours can leverage UK–India ties to scale. We also discussed the recently concluded UK–India Free Trade Agreement and learned about the support initiatives we can tap into to expand our presence in both regions.\n\xa0\nThe delegation met our teams, explored our workspace, and experienced our people-first culture firsthand. A truly inspiring exchange that strengthened meaningful connections.\n\xa0\n#BusinessConnections #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 day ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_coimbatore-businessconnections-saas-activity-7360988489535950874-Ko2S', 'urn': '7360988489535950874'}, {'attributes': [{'first': 'Saravanan', 'headline': 'Chief of Staff, Kovai.co | Helping Tech writers, Product teams & Support leaders to scale-up and streamline operations through using Document360', 'last': 'Balakrishnan', 'public_id': 'saravananbalakrishnan', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAA7HrKwBwv-aVVPKOjYi2bSxiBgWYBm2PJY'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQG34o1G5USP9g/feedshare-shrink_20/B56ZiYjG5CH0Aw-/0/1754906000862?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=c9_NFC7r98m57BnB_jtiYod177yb92CBjBoPJiZ6YOI'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQEp7laYS9geHg/feedshare-shrink_480/B56ZiYjG3uH0Ak-/0/1754906001714?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=WoQSoq4BK0TFlQZQhBh6aAyY_PomPs2urmuuocQg9BU'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGE7zjRbwXf9A/feedshare-shrink_800/B56ZiYjG4zH0Ak-/0/1754906000942?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=MbSEF1MjhD9HOajJZ0D0bhnyUryio4EP0Ia7ZxHvLkg'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_interests': 2, 'num_likes': 107, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-08-11 11:00:10', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Imagine turning an idea into a working app in just a few minutes - no code, no complex setup. We did not just talk about building apps - we built one, live in 5 minutes.\n\xa0\nIn Session 3 of CODE RED, Saravanan Balakrishnan, Chief of Staff, walked us through Lovable AI, a tool that turns prompts into real, working apps.\n\xa0\nNo coding. No heavy setup. Just smart, simple, and quick.\n\xa0\n#CodeRed #AI #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 days ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_codered-ai-saas-activity-7360626075166494720-F5ke', 'urn': '7360626075166494720'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Nilesh', 'headline': 'Product Specialist at Zoho', 'last': 'Kirti DN', 'public_id': 'nileshkirti', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAADDQPpIBZQMZ88kKrtKqIx_1DYQjlmoSkaU'}, {'first': 'Janani', 'headline': 'Associate Product Marketer at Kovai.co | Document360 | SaaS Marketing I B2B Marketing', 'last': 'Aishwarya', 'public_id': 'jananiaishwarya', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAADbBVYgBlo9prppjfgmUt93HhtfFrPz3J4E'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 4, 'num_empathy': 6, 'num_likes': 186, 'num_praises': 6, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-08-07 05:00:12', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Growth happens with people.\n\nWe have welcomed new talents to Kovai.co, and every one of them adds a new story to our journey.\n\xa0\nVijay Shakthivel | Nilesh Kirti DN | Janani Aishwarya | Kavin K G\n\n#NewBeginnings #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '6 days ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_new-joiners-at-kovaico-activity-7359085936892153857-Al8f', 'urn': '7359085936892153857'}, {'attributes': [{'first': 'Sailesh', 'headline': 'Data Scientist - Data Analyst| Machine Learning | NLP | GenAI | Computer Vision', 'last': 'Sivan ', 'public_id': 'sailesh-shocker', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAACYTPwQBxjbkdEbZZ2mKaMj1Gm4Q5Ed3F30'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFv4RzGJ6ubRA/feedshare-shrink_800/B56Zh0pK9sG0Ag-/0/1754303610934?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=vDcPjsEjic9e3tAMuaAU0NPWNvFrFh6pHpGGnnYBfc0'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGARjYztn2meQ/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56Zh0pK9uHQAo-/0/1754303612074?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=QUs0yB0poScx9Td7-80w0Ex725Fnvg5QMdTK65IH4kQ'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQHHpnflmNVMaQ/feedshare-shrink_160/B56Zh0pK.SG4Ac-/0/1754303616948?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=sp-SJsotrd0ulsbgcVGMSdjG90duSVXA75oDaJoZ95E'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 168, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-08-04 11:30:06', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Our second CODE RED session was all about turning data into dashboards!\n\xa0\nLed by Sailesh Sivan, Data Analyst, our team explored Power BI, learning how to build and customize dashboards, make reports look smarter, and pull insights in just minutes.\n\xa0\nFrom quick tips to best practices and a live demo, this session made data feel easy and actionable.\n\xa0\n#CodeRed #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 week ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_codered-saas-togetherwegrow-activity-7358096896269148160-Qnni', 'urn': '7358096896269148160'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQG_q5aYtCgz1A/feedshare-shrink_1280/B56ZhuPGfBHUAk-/0/1754196109952?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=gM2TFpisS0V0q85m9hZ-UWKLwmPX9DJDQWvNr5djbsA'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 89, 'num_praises': 1, 'num_reposts': 1, 'posted': '2025-08-03 05:00:03', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'At work, we share projects, meetings, and targets.\n\xa0\nBut the best part? We also share stories, snacks, and plenty of laughter with the friends we have found along the way.\n\xa0\nBecause work is better when it feels like working with friends.\n\xa0\nHappy Friendship Day from Kovai.co!\xa0\xa0🤝\n\xa0\n#FriendshipDay #PeopleFirst #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 week ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_friendshipday-peoplefirst-togetherwegrow-activity-7357636348658241539-VuHm', 'urn': '7357636348658241539'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFLh3qiPtItKw/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56Zhk2.cMHMAo-/0/1754038796386?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=oLVL2V9R3FmedUSRE7xLBN42OYggIJk9E87BNnr6zj8'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQE3v_ePylwmYw/feedshare-shrink_20/B56Zhk2.bFHkA0-/0/1754038793524?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=dL72mXfOtGtgU-KAQoO9IQFZnPkIcNZYKfEwEpnMn24'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGGJ9HOKFvr7g/feedshare-shrink_1280/B56Zhk2.aHHUAk-/0/1754038794938?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=rA5QRlsTnJMS3ALGACeth5VDd675_8nGCUr0jHmZTtk'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFG8uuegl6POw/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56Zhk2.a7HkAo-/0/1754038792967?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=h9xpYVbgh8lQW4mVkco-Do-7fuhdF98iSk0GlKPY9z8'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQE4Eo4bt-nIsA/feedshare-shrink_160/B56Zhk2.cQG0Ao-/0/1754038794693?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=RZ7Cwx2aAA4PQT2wGYZp6VET8EfGTA8LCqPmQrK1hGk'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGQS0GX66XSXg/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56Zhk2.cOHMAs-/0/1754038795399?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=kYN_YkXfzdOpbaBE7bAmCfQROLtOOXzADFL6-H10eks'}], 'num_appreciations': 2, 'num_comments': 3, 'num_likes': 190, 'num_praises': 5, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-08-01 11:30:09', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Leadership goes beyond tasks, it’s about people, inspiration, and the culture we create together.\n\xa0\nOur first Manager Mastery session at Kovai.co gave our People Managers and Team Leads a chance to slow down, reflect on their journey, and see the real impact they have on their teams.\n\xa0\nThis is the beginning of a journey that will grow both our leaders and our culture. 🌱\n\xa0\n#GrowingLaeders #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 week ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_growinglaeders-saas-togetherwegrow-activity-7357009743606935552-uW-a', 'urn': '7357009743606935552'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Selvaraaju', 'headline': 'Business Strategy | Innovation | Data Science | AI', 'last': 'Murugesan', 'public_id': 'selvaraaju', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABrSbf4B6GO5K2BcJrnWaRbqcPjyGH97pYU'}, {'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGbxPh3ciybDw/feedshare-shrink_160/B56ZhPPpM9H0Ag-/0/1753676161277?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=Oz6pM0nIeRC5u6wVQrXkcfzxKyT8soyFd4hyy6eRW-g'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGnd6U4Vr1vSw/feedshare-shrink_160/B56ZhPPpLXH0Ag-/0/1753676160825?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=rnExyDssxkaNycPFz1t0qskW3q2aEgINOBabTfJt46c'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFm3Jcc1Hae1g/feedshare-shrink_480/B56ZhPPpMXHUAY-/0/1753676161097?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=ooj6QWhYCUceJywaRaQgtX5yehT7T7OqQ8Pp3JN7pXE'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQG-INW10xPP1Q/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56ZhPPpMPH0Ao-/0/1753676160946?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=eimRDc7TL8ZKOxBm4WRydP0Tb63d7vPCtLLb255otp4'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 2, 'num_interests': 3, 'num_likes': 224, 'num_praises': 1, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-07-28 05:00:02', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': "Last Friday, we had our very first CODE RED session at Kovai.co  - a new series where we explore AI as a company.\n\nSelvaraaju Murugesan, the head of Data Science at Kovai.co led the session on prompt engineering, helping us understand how AI assistants work, how to ask better questions to AI, and how to implement them wisely in our workflow.\n\xa0\nThis is more than just tools and tricks. It's about building confidence and clarity as we step into the world of #AI, together.\n\xa0\n#CodeRed #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow", 'time': '2 weeks ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_ai-codered-saas-activity-7355462014002974722-kb0U', 'urn': '7355462014002974722'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQHCTI_nhEZ6BA/feedshare-shrink_160/B56ZhAGa1gG4Ak-/0/1753422085243?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=yB9psRP54TNMioNYRcMw4tU4EKZuHywVu9rCu7mwUiA'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 49, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-07-25 09:30:03', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': '🚨Kovai.co’s CODE RED\n\nIt’s not just a program, it’s a long-term movement to upskill, innovate, and embed AI into everything we do.\n\xa0\nIn a world where AI is rewriting the rules of #SaaS, this initiative of 10 sessions is designed to equip every Kovaiite, across every department, with practical AI skills. From what’s buzzing in AI right now to how it fits into our SaaS workflows, each session is designed to help us connect the dots and stay ahead.\n\nWe are not just watching the future unfold, we are building it together.\n\xa0\n#CodeRed #AI #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 weeks ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_saas-codered-ai-activity-7354442803122229249-3iKC', 'urn': '7354442803122229249'}, {'attributes': [{'first': 'Saravana', 'headline': 'CEO @ Kovai.co (Products: Document360, Turbo360, BizTalk360)', 'last': 'Kumar', 'public_id': 'saravanamv', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAAAkdAgBhkMkKNNRxdWwogrN4jIXXSuPCUc'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 2, 'num_empathy': 5, 'num_interests': 1, 'num_likes': 99, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-07-24 12:31:41', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Plan B? Not as a Founder\n\xa0\nHear it straight from our CEO and Founder, Saravana Kumar, about why unwavering conviction and belief are more important than backup plans, especially when navigating the highs and lows of building a company.\n\xa0\nCheck out the full video - https://lnkd.in/gvrJPT4r\n\xa0\n#conviction #foundersinsights #togetherwegrow', 'time': '2 weeks ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_conviction-foundersinsights-togetherwegrow-activity-7354126125813391362-duNG', 'urn': '7354126125813391362', 'video': {'duration': 42533, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQFTLk6JhR8O4w/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56Zg8anMNHQB0-/0/1753360295111?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=N1AIocb91Vo4tBoC-C3fvpoifVzkVJVrni9g8n6GaPI'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 2, 'num_empathy': 14, 'num_likes': 278, 'num_praises': 1, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-07-17 13:00:19', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': '🙂💻☕🎯🍱💬🧠✅🙌🍰\n\nWork feels lighter when your day looks like this.\nCoffee breaks that turn into conversations. Carrom matches between code pushes.\xa0Celebrations for every win.\n\nAnd teammates who make it all worthwhile.\n\xa0\nThis isn’t just a workplace, it’s Kovai.co. 😄\n\xa0\n#WorldEmojiDay #Kovaico #BestPlaceToWork #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '3 weeks ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_worldemojiday-kovaico-bestplacetowork-activity-7351596616694292481-ZmPU', 'urn': '7351596616694292481', 'video': {'duration': 58933, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQEqs9ldUeDesg/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZgYbS_5H0B0-/0/1752756529249?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=fbE9TyOV7pgeIhd7_eWylfEE-1S0maV7J2Z26ahohVE'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Swathi', 'headline': 'Account Executive (APAC) - Document360- The Knowledge Base Platform, engineered for growing companies', 'last': 'Selvaraj', 'public_id': 'swathi-selvaraj-36a228105', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABqNQgIBw4miFNQ3fZs-uR3fw2H5F6QysOY'}, {'first': 'Gowtham', 'headline': 'Senior Creative Designer at Kovai.co', 'last': 'M', 'public_id': 'gowtham-m-a7b99254', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAAuJGH8Brd5r2CevBt00dTbqg5zTEddqDoE'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 4, 'num_likes': 70, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-07-15 05:00:41', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Every journey is personal.\n\nBut when a company truly values its people, the impact goes far beyond the paycheck.\n\xa0\nAt Kovai.co, the Together We Grow Bonus is not just a reward, it’s a promise kept.\xa0\n\xa0\nA thank you for the loyalty, hard work, and heart our people put in every day. ✨ \n\nSwathi Selvaraj | Gowtham M\n\xa0\n#TogetherWeGrow #Peoplefirst #Sharingsuccess', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_togetherwegrow-peoplefirst-sharingsuccess-activity-7350751137987276800-NtaE', 'urn': '7350751137987276800', 'video': {'duration': 48200, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQE4IqVF_5Wx_Q/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZgMdFRiHMBw-/0/1752555636842?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=ENq3LwgbxYh48vi6lewuVEWee6zb6t8lEK99oruMAyY'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '11381804', 'name': 'Document360', 'public_id': 'document360', 'type': 'company'}, {'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQF5kMLYUkCPNQ/feedshare-shrink_480/B56Zftkke9GoAg-/0/1752037479873?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=OXjuYHNlw3lt__8PUltcsdqe7cM3DT-JWsI4PI2UEYI'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFiI3t-NT3pRQ/feedshare-shrink_800/B56Zftkke5HQAk-/0/1752037479846?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=3RiBp4V6zYxzCtlQhCf2aKotluFIRnPAvyowi1vNwq0'}, {'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQHziquUNQC71Q/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56Zftkkd2IAAo-/0/1752037478717?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=dUOeSEA5aDGEmqtWzun0zNxye_0fERjuO5J79GnDYPE'}], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 7, 'num_empathy': 14, 'num_likes': 763, 'num_praises': 13, 'num_reposts': 3, 'posted': '2025-07-09 05:04:41', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': '50 features in, and going strong! ⚡\n\xa0\nOur latest addition, Eddy AI Writing Agent in Document360, brings speed and intelligence to documentation like never before.\n\nEarlier this week, we marked the moment with a cake-cutting evening to celebrate this milestone at Kovai.co.\xa0\n\xa0\nGrateful for the journey so far, and even more excited for what lies ahead!\n\xa0\n#AI #SaaS #Kovaico #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_ai-saas-kovaico-activity-7348577818542297088-KWli', 'urn': '7348577818542297088'}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 4, 'num_comments': 28, 'num_empathy': 19, 'num_interests': 1, 'num_likes': 326, 'num_praises': 29, 'num_reposts': 20, 'posted': '2025-07-08 07:19:15', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/saravanamv', 'name': 'Saravana Kumar'}, 'reshared': True, 'text': '"50 AI features in 50 months"\n\nWe shipped our first AI Feature, "SEO Metadata Generator", 50 months ago, even before the AI and ChatGPT wave started.\n\nAround January 2023, when ChatGPT became mainstream, it was very clear to us that it was going to redefine the way certain industries operate. We understood that "Knowledge management, Knowledge base" is going to go through a massive shift.\n\nWe were curious and swiftly changed our direction to be "AI first". \n\nWe have incrementally shipped many AI features for the past couple of years, and we mandated that at least 2-3 AI features be included\xa0in every release (we have a monthly release cadence). \n\nLast weekend was a milestone moment for us, releasing our 50th AI feature, not just a small incremental one, but a game-changing "AI Writing Agent" that will redefine how documentation will be created in the future.\n\nWe took a step back, analysed the current workflow used by human authors today to create content, and asked ourselves how AI can help this process by giving them superpowers. \n\nWriters didn\'t have to begin from scratch anymore; they had a thinking buddy within the product. And the feedback we got was incredibly positive. To many of our customers, it was like we had endowed them with superpowers.   \n\nThat\'s the outcome of our first true AI agent (watch the video). \n\nIt was built thoughtfully and with the clear intention of keeping "Humans in the loop" and security and privacy at its heart.\n\nOur ambition is to make people (knowledge base creators) focus on creative work rather than mundane tasks. We are leveraging AI to achieve that mission.\n\nThis is just the beginning; more AI agents are coming to Document360.\n\nComing next\n\n🚀 AI Reviewer Agent - Will help review and provide feedback according to your policy and style guide.\n\n🚀 AI Feedback Agent - React to end users feedback on your knowledge base.  \n\xa0\nMy heartfelt thanks to: \n\n* Our product team, thank you for staying curious and exploring further.\n\n* Our customers, thank you for believing in what we are creating, and\n\n* To all the technical writers using Document360, we are creating this for you, and we\'re just getting started.\n\xa0\nHere\'s to the next 50.\xa0👏', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/saravanamv_50-ai-features-in-50-months-we-shipped-ugcPost-7348231073429921792-mNHT', 'urn': '7348249294145036288', 'video': {'duration': 112333, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D4E05AQGjb_Be9oiXLQ/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B4EZfopOiBHYB0-/0/1751954861415?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=jmX2cJWioEdWMcyUxkRHUiNyFBC5XyoXNEttMmMNvbE'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '11381804', 'name': 'Document360', 'public_id': 'document360', 'type': 'company'}, {'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 140, 'num_praises': 6, 'num_reposts': 1, 'posted': '2025-07-07 12:30:29', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': "Did someone say 50th feature? 🎉\n\nYes, and it's a big one!\n\xa0\nWe are proud to unveil Eddy AI Writing Agent in Document360 - our 50th feature release and a milestone moment for everyone at Kovai.co.\n\xa0\nThis one’s built to solve a real challenge faced by the documentation teams, the time-consuming process of turning product knowledge into publish-ready content.\n\xa0\nWith Eddy AI Writing Agent, technical writers can now generate first drafts in minutes, all while staying aligned with corporate style guides, templates, and tone. Whether it's extracting insights from meeting recordings or automating SEO-friendly structure, this new feature handles the heavy lifting so writers can focus on crafting high-quality content.\n\xa0\n📖 Dive into the full story and see how this feature is reshaping content creation: https://lnkd.in/gH-NzdCq\n\nCheck out the feature: https://lnkd.in/gpDvkt3y\n\xa0\n#AI #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow", 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_eddy-ai-writing-agent-activity-7347965231991570438-Ova0', 'urn': '7347965231991570438'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 2, 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 265, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-07-05 11:00:02', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Yesterday we had students from Dr. G.R.D. School of Commerce and International Business, Coimbatore, visit Kovai.co for a Customer Success internship drive.\n\nAround 20 students participated, and soon, a few of them will begin their internship journey with us.\n\nLooking forward to having them on board and learning together.\n\n#CustomerSuccess #Internship #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_customer-success-internship-drive-activity-7347217691662761985-Wld2', 'urn': '7347217691662761985'}, {'article_subtitle': 'kovai.co', 'article_title': 'AI-Powered Marketing: Achieving More with Less', 'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 1, 'num_likes': 23, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-07-01 12:30:03', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'AI helps you think faster.\nAutomation helps you work smarter.\nTogether, they are reshaping the future of marketing.\n\xa0\nOur recent blog covers where to begin, why it matters for #marketing teams, and what pitfalls to watch out for.\nHere’s how to embrace it the smart way.\n\xa0\n👉 Read the full blog - https://lnkd.in/gat5Wkq8\n\xa0\n#AI #Automation #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_ai-powered-marketing-achieving-more-with-activity-7345790794714271744-e-Pv', 'urn': '7345790794714271744'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Venkatesh', 'headline': 'Senior Growth Marketer @ Kovai.co 📊 Performance-Driven B2B SaaS | Delivering Measurable ROI & Quality MQLs 🎯 Igniting Growth for Document360 and Turbo360', 'last': 'Regupathy Sreedharan', 'public_id': 'venkirs', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABBolgcBlM892mK6Dw2uEbM9cSbca-KARCU'}, {'first': 'Senthilkumar', 'headline': 'Senior Engineering Manager at Kovai.co', 'last': 'Palanisamy', 'public_id': 'senthilkumarpalanisamy', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAAKuZ_UBMBa7N9wpi9OqR-b4Ol0IQm87h68'}], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 1, 'num_empathy': 3, 'num_likes': 80, 'num_praises': 1, 'num_reposts': 1, 'posted': '2025-06-30 13:01:22', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Together We Grow Bonus at Kovai.co helped our people to prepay a home loan, support son’s education, and gave one parent the confidence to plan daughter’s future in the long term.\n\n It’s these quiet wins that mean the most, and we are glad to be a part of it.\n\nVenkatesh | Senthilkumar\n\n #TogetherWeGrow #Peoplefirst #Sharingsuccess', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_togetherwegrow-peoplefirst-sharingsuccess-activity-7345436288688234498-ANlL', 'urn': '7345436288688234498', 'video': {'duration': 52466, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQG4N_a5rCnpig/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZfA7HIIHUB8-/0/1751288479264?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=bur9XwoHVe86Z_TD0fx5Bm2MY0q4TFrM8l8u4x2gDUQ'}}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 5, 'num_empathy': 7, 'num_likes': 168, 'num_praises': 4, 'num_reposts': 4, 'posted': '2025-06-28 06:00:02', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'There are events you attend, and then there are ones you feel.\n\nKovision 2025 was that kind of day for everyone of us. 🌟 \n\xa0\nIt was a celebration of everything we have built together.\n\xa0\nHere’s the full video that captures the heart of it all. \n\nGrateful to everyone who brought their energy, talent, and spirit to make it what it was. 👏 \n\xa0\n#Kovision #Kovaico #AnnualMeet #LifeAtKovai #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_kovision-2025-activity-7344605478171119618-QDb_', 'urn': '7344605478171119618', 'video': {'duration': 57333, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQEnM5v66v1YCA/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56Ze1EQsUHUB0-/0/1751089538562?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=X-zGMw1EcAG1Z0OxSz9Wrgio3STJdzLmE94idiQUdHQ'}}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 9, 'num_interests': 1, 'num_likes': 175, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-06-26 12:00:01', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Swipe through a gallery of moments we wish we could frame! 🖼️ \n\nWe played games, cheered for 100+ awardees, and ended on a high note, literally.\n\nKovision 2025\xa0✨ \n\n\xa0\n🎞️ More behind these memories? It’s all on the blog.\nDive into it!\n\n🔗 https://lnkd.in/gczRcjBV\n\xa0\n#Kovision #Kovaico #AnnualMeet #LifeAtKovai #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_kovision-2025-activity-7343971296495472641-_dwt', 'urn': '7343971296495472641'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '11678446', 'name': 'Turbo360', 'public_id': 'turbo360cloud', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 1, 'num_likes': 48, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-06-23 11:30:07', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': '#INTEGRATE2025, our flagship event, just wrapped up a few days ago, and it was truly something to remember!\n\xa0\nIt’s been 13 years of bringing the Microsoft Integration community together, and this year was no different.\n\xa0\nHere’s a quick look at some of the standout moments from the event.\nWant to see more? Explore our detailed event blogs below.\n\xa0\nDay 1 Highlights - https://lnkd.in/gSs-nnrd\nDay 2 Highlights - https://lnkd.in/gJ4eu_v5\n\nTurbo360\n\xa0\n#Turbo360 #Kovaico #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_integrate-2025-activity-7342876607792992257-MYtM', 'urn': '7342876607792992257'}, {'article_subtitle': 'kovai.co', 'article_title': 'From Interns to Impact Makers in Data Science at Kovai.co', 'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Sriharan', 'headline': 'Associate Data Analyst @ Kovai.co | Machine Learning | Data science| Python | Msc Statistics| PSGCAS', 'last': 'T', 'public_id': 'sriharan-t', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAC5qW_4B7tXeLkT72pnJ5XZbfosM5Lgf-Ts'}, {'first': 'Aishwarya', 'headline': 'AI/ML Enthusiast | GenAI & LLMs | Python • Prompt Engineering • OpenAI • Data Pipelines', 'last': 'N M', 'public_id': 'aishwarya-n-m', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAERa-gIB_8j5XyFIsICrRO3FMU90XU8W0QA'}, {'company_id': '11381804', 'name': 'Document360', 'public_id': 'document360', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_likes': 76, 'num_praises': 3, 'num_reposts': 1, 'posted': '2025-06-20 11:30:08', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Ever wondered what our Kovai.co interns actually build?\n\xa0\nTwo interns from our Data Science team, Sriharan T and Aishwarya N M are the minds behind some of our most exciting #AI features in Document360. 🚀\n\xa0\nRead their 6-month #internship journey! 👇\n\xa0\n🔗 https://lnkd.in/g7E7Z6kE\n\xa0\n#SaaS #DataScience #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_from-interns-to-impact-makers-in-data-science-activity-7341789450168868867-Sni5', 'urn': '7341789450168868867'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '783611', 'name': 'MongoDB', 'public_id': 'mongodbinc', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E22AQGKyRicJmWpBA/feedshare-shrink_160/B4EZeL_HWAHIAg-/0/1750400271214?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=3RzNJBYfld5rTV-9eHzI7PDRGAcz2eeFCftjmwinqhc'}], 'num_comments': 1, 'num_interests': 2, 'num_likes': 24, 'num_reposts': 3, 'posted': '2025-06-20 10:32:09', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/document360/posts', 'name': 'Document360'}, 'reshared': True, 'text': '"𝗜 𝗱𝗼𝗻’𝘁 𝗸𝗻𝗼𝘄" 𝘀𝗵𝗼𝘂𝗹𝗱𝗻’𝘁 𝗯𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝘁𝗯𝗼𝘁’𝘀 𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗼𝗻 𝗿𝗲𝗽𝗹𝘆. 𝗪𝗲 𝗳𝗶𝘅𝗲𝗱 𝘁𝗵𝗮𝘁, 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲’𝘀 𝗵𝗼𝘄.\n\xa0\nAt Document360, we faced the same challenge. Despite our Eddy AI chatbot doing an excellent job at understanding keywords, many users were typing keywords instead of complete questions, meaning the chatbot would either miss the context or answer with an I don\'t know.\n\n So, we levelled up.\n\n We integrated MongoDB Hybrid Search combining:\n\xa0\n✅ Keyword search (Atlas Search)\n✅ Vector search for semantic accuracy\n✅ RRF reranking for better context\n✅ Powered by GPT-4.1 mini\n\nToday, Eddy AI provides faster, more accurate responses, even when the user types in a keyword-only query.\n\nWe are also exploring more advanced GenAI functionality such as $rankfusion and Voyage AI embeddings to push the next step even further.\n\nInterested in knowing how we did it?\n\xa0\nFull story in our new blog - link in the comments.\n\n#documentation #MongoDB #chatbots #genai', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/document360_documentation-mongodb-chatbots-activity-7341710864892256257-khr3', 'urn': '7341774855337320450'}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 6, 'num_likes': 88, 'num_praises': 1, 'num_reposts': 1, 'posted': '2025-06-19 13:00:16', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'One day. So many moments.\nYes, it’s the most awaited event of the year - KOVISION 2025✨ \n\nHere’s a tiny peek into a day packed with joy, stories, and everything in between that made us smile a little wider.\n\nSave your excitement, this is only part one. \n\nFull video coming up! 🔥 \n\n#Kovision #Kovaico #AnnualMeet #LifeAtKovai #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '1 month ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_kovision-kovaico-annualmeet-activity-7341449744944140291-RJW-', 'urn': '7341449744944140291', 'video': {'duration': 45333, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQFnT8MebX89OA/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZeIM3JAGoBo-/0/1750336775679?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=8jeJZKjYggkWw5RvUYrNTyXSkY10JCF3PUih3Gps6HU'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Nekalya', 'headline': 'Software Engineer QA', 'last': 'K', 'public_id': 'nekalya-k-a97260181', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAACruFBMBMLz4nysDe6rsWMWeCIxdyhSaqvo'}, {'first': 'Sai', 'headline': 'A passionate professional', 'last': 'D.', 'public_id': 'sai-dheepika', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAB1ARHwBUBGNotKBaMBpY7BDw-a-BuaOvfo'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 1, 'num_empathy': 2, 'num_likes': 58, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-18 11:30:17', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Not needing to ask. Not waiting for the right time.\nThis Together We Grow Bonus at Kovai.co gave our people the power to act, whether it was contributing to a new home or handling wedding expenses independently.\n\n And for us, that’s the kind of support that matters.\n\nNekalya K | Sai D.\n\xa0\n#TogetherWeGrow #Peoplefirst #Sharingsuccess', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_togetherwegrow-peoplefirst-sharingsuccess-activity-7341064712790450176-GLb-', 'urn': '7341064712790450176', 'video': {'duration': 56733, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQHeIl4JBLciPA/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZeCtSkjH8Bk-/0/1750244632264?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=4A1AAA2TzTAVkMNxJMBBYT9psp-gOqtKIY4Wdy7CFeU'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Saranya', 'headline': 'Release Coordinator| QA Specialist| Technical Writer', 'last': 'Ramakrishnan', 'public_id': 'saranya-ramakrishnan-2a644496', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABRasJ4BELJucA_QnaQfTzpnCtuHLxqchHw'}, {'first': 'Vishnu', 'headline': 'Working as Technical Architect at Kovai Limited for SAAS product Document360.', 'last': 'Balachandran', 'public_id': 'vishnub5', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABce-msBuCtdJuuV1RzF_8cMWJWuF0GkIGI'}, {'first': 'Kuzhali', 'headline': 'Lead SDET', 'last': 'Maheshwaran', 'public_id': 'kuzhali-maheshwaran-86ba9349', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAApN-hMB7RN6KbFB6HA908roNC9IIYk5Tsc'}, {'first': 'Sivaramakrishnan', 'headline': 'Lead Product Support Engineer | Expert in Azure Management & Customer Success | BizTalk | Cloud | Enhancing B2B On-Prem & SaaS Product Efficiency by 35%', 'last': 'Arumugam', 'public_id': 'sivaramakrishnan-aru', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABfLregBOU9Yi5v83xLCvCDKxkCxSDr6bAE'}, {'first': 'Indhirani', 'headline': 'Manager - Finance & Operations at Kovai.co', 'last': 'Rangasamy', 'public_id': 'indhirani-rangasamy-878ab8108', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABs3LdwBGr7L8x2HSaIUbMnEGlghCpe38hc'}], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 11, 'num_empathy': 31, 'num_likes': 434, 'num_praises': 26, 'num_reposts': 4, 'posted': '2025-06-18 08:46:27', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/saravanamv', 'name': 'Saravana Kumar'}, 'reshared': True, 'text': 'KOVISION2025\n\nRight after wrapping up our INTEGRATE 2025 event in London last Tuesday, I flew to India for something that always recharges me - our annual cultural festival, KOVISION2025.\n\nWe marked 14 years of Kovai.co. \n\nThis time, a big part of our UK team joined the celebrations in person. \n\nAt Kovai.co, fun and purpose go hand in hand. KOVISION is our way of pressing pause, celebrating what we’ve built, and looking ahead with fresh energy.\n\nThe energy on the day was something else. Weeks of preparation led to an evening filled with music, laughter, dance, and moments that reminded us why we do what we do.\n\nThe team had put together a video showcasing my journey building Kovai.co from the ground up to express their gratitude, love and affection. They took footage from my parents, kids, close friends, and various team members. It was a very emotional moment, not just for me, but for many people who travelled along this 14-year-long journey. \n\nThey created a very special memento and asked my parent to present it. I was deeply moved, and the words felt short to express my feelings.\n\nWe also unveiled a beautifully designed "Kovai.co Story Book" - a physical snapshot of our journey, values, and milestones. I\'ll share more about it\xa0in the coming days.\n\nI\'m proud to witness 5 of our team members crossing the special "10 years at Kovai.co" milestone. Thanks to Saranya Ramakrishnan, Vishnu Balachandran, Kuzhali Maheshwaran, Sivaramakrishnan Arumugam and Indhirani Rangasamy for your commitment and dedication to being part of the journey.\n\nEvery time I stand on that stage, I’m reminded: the people make Kovai.co what it is.\n\nHuge congratulations to everyone who received their excellence and service awards.\n\nHere’s to many more milestones and moments that matter.\n\n#TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/saravanamv_togetherwegrow-ugcPost-7341005787743338496-RCs6', 'urn': '7341023480752066560', 'video': {'duration': 45333, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQEUTOSzpqn0lA/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZeB93inGQBg-/0/1750232200374?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=-MGikgt1uecAHg6VSEbZjscJqu48CKbe-crkEOzWDmc'}}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQEUHSPlmFJ-0w/feedshare-shrink_160/B56Zd5vZOsHoAc-/0/1750094159191?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=2r06x5TPpSs6xJmkZ9elSPb9HdK8zXNjzX_1yKTKqx4'}], 'num_comments': 1, 'num_empathy': 3, 'num_likes': 35, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-06-17 09:59:45', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/turbo360cloud/posts', 'name': 'Turbo360'}, 'reshared': True, 'text': 'INTEGRATE over the years tells a story — Of how a small gathering grew into a global stage for integration, innovation, and intelligent automation.\n\xa0\nFrom BizTalk to Azure.\nFrom hybrid to agentic workflows.\nFrom conversations in corridors to keynotes that shape the future.\n\xa0\nEvery edition has been a chapter.\nAnd together, we’ve written a story of progress, passion, and people.\n\xa0\nINTEGRATE 2025 just added another unforgettable chapter.\n\xa0\nHere’s to the journey so far — and to what’s next. 🚀\n\xa0\n#Azure #AzureAI #INTEGRATE2025 #AIS', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/turbo360cloud_azure-azureai-integrate2025-activity-7340426940492804096-XfA1', 'urn': '7340679538642718721'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFv30qnUcI91g/feedshare-shrink_160/B56Zdx.eRfH8Ac-/0/1749963895742?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=UycPHUvVdfY_R1hGgfr_Ss444a7_dvYWdRz1EZqnZuU'}], 'num_comments': 1, 'num_empathy': 5, 'num_likes': 112, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-15 05:04:56', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Our Kovai.co team is proudly powered by the Dads - engineers, leaders, and mentors who bring the same dedication to work and home.\n\n Wishing a Happy Father’s Day to everyone, balancing sprints and story time.\n\xa0\n#FathersDay #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_fathersday-saas-togetherwegrow-activity-7339880572493713408-dzTX', 'urn': '7339880572493713408'}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 50, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-13 08:25:40', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Before the stage lights turn on, here’s everything that’s lined up for today.\n\nKovision 2025 is a celebration of everything we are at Kovai.co.\n\xa0\nHere we go!\n\xa0\n#AnnualMeet #Kovaico #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_annualmeet-kovaico-togetherwegrow-activity-7339206312704077825-k61T', 'urn': '7339206312704077825', 'video': {'duration': 52766, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQGO0hpR6kZLig/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZdoYuS_HoBo-/0/1749803136200?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=kSflDXFogVF98UDR5VkPn0W5cTRv1129_3HmxzNsAkc'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_likes': 24, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-13 05:45:08', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'What a couple of days it was!\n\nAs the Kovai.co team behind it, we are still smiling about everything that happened at #INTEGRATE2025.\n\nHere’s a quick look back at what made it so special.', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_integrate-2025-activity-7339165909778931712-NTZE', 'urn': '7339165909778931712'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGW2P4ZfRZmUw/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56ZdinmPmGoAo-/0/1749706239104?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=iLJ0zYidmLJMSJa_G5HmRXE3VpLYJ7ZlNrPiON3YJPU'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 5, 'num_likes': 120, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-12 05:30:39', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Our story isn’t just about products and progress. 🌟 \n\nIt’s about people, purpose, and everything in between.\n\nCatch the launch of "The Kovai.co Storybook" at Kovision 2025. Stay tuned!\n\xa0\n#Storybook #Unfold #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_storybook-unfold-togetherwegrow-activity-7338799878518489118-WEwx', 'urn': '7338799878518489118'}, {'article_subtitle': 'turbo360.com', 'article_title': 'INTEGRATE 2025 Day 2 Highlights - Turbo360', 'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_likes': 4, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-06-11 05:35:40', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/turbo360cloud/posts', 'name': 'Turbo360'}, 'reshared': True, 'text': 'Wrapping up #INTEGRATE2025 with our recap blog!\n\nTwo days of innovation, inspiration, and deep dives into the future of integration — powered by passionate minds from across the globe. 🌍\n\nFollow the link for Day 2 highlights - https://lnkd.in/gjEkbYvE\n\n#INTEGRATE2025\xa0#AzureIntegration #Turbo360 #TechCommunity #Azure #AzureAI', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/turbo360cloud_integrate-2025-day-2-highlights-turbo360-activity-7338244142684061696-RZN4', 'urn': '7338438753109057536'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '11678446', 'name': 'Turbo360', 'public_id': 'turbo360cloud', 'type': 'company'}, {'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_likes': 33, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-11 05:20:08', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'What an incredible two days it has been!\n\nAs the team behind Turbo360 and the proud organizers of #INTEGRATE2025, we at Kovai.co are grateful to see the global integration community come together with such passion and purpose.\n\nA heartfelt thank you to our speakers, sponsors, partners, and every attendee who made this event one to remember. \n\nHere’s to pushing boundaries and building the future of integration, together.', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_integrate2025-thankyou-eventwrap-activity-7338434842902073344-3pxX', 'urn': '7338434842902073344'}, {'article_subtitle': 'turbo360.com', 'article_title': 'INTEGRATE 2025 Day 1 Highlights | Key Announcements & Takeaways', 'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_likes': 10, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-06-10 04:59:05', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/turbo360cloud/posts', 'name': 'Turbo360'}, 'reshared': True, 'text': 'And that’s a wrap on Day 1 of #INTEGRATE2025!\n\n💡 Insights shared. \n🤝 Partnerships formed. \n🔥 Innovation ignited. \n\nTomorrow’s lineup? Even more stacked. Same time, same place. Let’s go again! \n\nRead the key highlights of today at - https://lnkd.in/gSs-nnrd\n\n#Azure #AzureAI #AIS #Azurecommunity', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/turbo360cloud_integrate-2025-day-1-highlights-key-announcements-activity-7337913187377258497-RNGB', 'urn': '7338067157911556096'}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 7, 'num_likes': 79, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-09 12:00:03', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Here’s what Kovision 2025, our Annual Meet, looks like before the curtain rises!\n\nMissed steps, laughs, retakes, and that “one more time” energy.\n\nThe big day’s almost here.\n\xa0\n#Kovision2025 #AnnualMeet #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_kovision2025-annualmeet-togetherwegrow-activity-7337810711340847104-9u6m', 'urn': '7337810711340847104', 'video': {'duration': 30533, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQF7x6bwLkD2zQ/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZdUcUmFHoBQ-/0/1749468423041?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=McHbQXN2EpAmkiMEVmB7X6VUdQ_bpzAEeq51YDQwaA0'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQEiOhgmCQca_w/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56ZdUDCrtGoAo-/0/1749461773551?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=RgLtltQiAJG1jcgYRBBbKoKS-fhPzLSe4puA2XuuX7U'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_likes': 13, 'num_praises': 1, 'num_reposts': 1, 'posted': '2025-06-09 11:23:22', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/turbo360cloud/posts', 'name': 'Turbo360'}, 'reshared': True, 'text': '📸 INTEGRATE Through the Years!\n\nFrom bold ideas to unforgettable moments — this banner tells the story.\n\nEvery photo here captures how far the integration community has come.\n\nCome take a walk down memory lane and spot your favorite year!\n\nKovai.co\n\n#INTEGRATE2025 #MicrosoftIntegration #CommunityMoments #ThrowbackWall #TechEvents', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/turbo360cloud_integrate2025-microsoftintegration-communitymoments-activity-7337774521099108352-Nqdd', 'urn': '7337801480227233793'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQGoZbeXOFH16g/feedshare-shrink_2048_1536/B56ZdTyuCkHEAs-/0/1749457497188?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=YBjdE5WBgUnpZJfM66mlWJ2VdeI5R8wo-oWgXHqi2vE'}], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 2, 'num_likes': 48, 'num_praises': 3, 'num_reposts': 5, 'posted': '2025-06-09 09:12:35', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/turbo360cloud/posts', 'name': 'Turbo360'}, 'reshared': True, 'text': 'Look at that crowd! The room is almost full, and the buzz is real. \n\n#INTEGRATE2025 is in full swing!\n\nKovai.co', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/turbo360cloud_integrate2025-activity-7337756583034089472-0Svx', 'urn': '7337768565690781696'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '11678446', 'name': 'Turbo360', 'public_id': 'turbo360cloud', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 33, 'num_reposts': 1, 'posted': '2025-06-09 08:31:39', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'The wait is over! #INTEGRATE2025 kicks off today!\n\nStay tuned and follow Turbo360 for more updates.', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_integrate2025-azure-azureai-activity-7337758264102670337-6Ftm', 'urn': '7337758264102670337'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '14670875', 'name': 'SRI KRISHNA COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING AND TECHNOLOGY', 'public_id': 'sri-krishna-college-of-engineering-and-technology-official', 'type': 'company'}, {'company_id': '13319947', 'name': 'Sri Eshwar College of Engineering', 'public_id': 'srieshwar', 'type': 'company'}, {'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 2, 'num_comments': 4, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_likes': 354, 'num_praises': 5, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-05 12:00:02', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'The next wave of data enthusiasts is here!\n\nThrough our recent internship drive, students from different colleges joined us to explore what it means to work in real-world data science. \n\nWe had fresh minds from SRI KRISHNA COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING AND TECHNOLOGY, Coimbatore, Dr. Mahalingam College of Engineering and Technology, Pollachi, and Sri Eshwar College of Engineering, Coimbatore.\n\nTheir 6-month journey at Kovai.co begins soon, and we are just as excited as they are.\n\n#datascience #internship #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_data-science-internship-2025-activity-7336361154568458241-1NeZ', 'urn': '7336361154568458241'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '11678446', 'name': 'Turbo360', 'public_id': 'turbo360cloud', 'type': 'company'}, {'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_likes': 21, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-06-05 09:42:01', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'As the proud force behind Turbo360, we at Kovai.co are excited to see INTEGRATE 2025 just around the corner!\n\nFrom our internal teams to the global tech community, this event is more than just a conference, it’s where #Microsoft Integration leaders connect, share, and shape the future.\n\nStay tuned for the big day!\n\n#INTEGRATE2025 #TechEvent #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_integrate2025-azureintegration-techevent-activity-7336326422384300032-lutr', 'urn': '7336326422384300032'}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 1, 'num_likes': 9, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-05-30 05:30:45', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'The #SaaS world is moving faster, and with every leap in technology, we are seeing new trends reshape how businesses build, scale, and deliver value.\n\xa0\nDrop your views in the\xa0comments! \n\xa0\n#SaaSTrends #AI #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_saas-saastrends-ai-activity-7334088860911509504-_3EJ', 'urn': '7334088860911509504'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [{'url': 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5622AQFNdmC6h3KLig/feedshare-shrink_20/B56ZcQC6J2HoAw-/0/1748320888863?e=1758153600&v=beta&t=xGziRBRH-Xzh0cv1NrahgB3CF_akhW49coZKa1UuYow'}], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 2, 'num_likes': 73, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-05-27 05:00:02', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'They are the ones behind every product launch, every headline, and every lead.\xa0🚀 \n\nToday, we raise a toast to all our marketers who keep Kovai.co moving forward.\n\nHappy #WorldMarketingDay! \n\n\xa0\n#Marketing #SaaS #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '2 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_worldmarketingday-marketing-saas-activity-7332993967199854593-GAze', 'urn': '7332993967199854593'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Gayathri', 'headline': 'Lead - Sales Development | Kovai.co | Document360', 'last': 'R', 'public_id': 'gayathri-r-1827789a', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABUdYfIB12b7djUARa7tTngAAQKA9VuyfgU'}, {'first': 'Logesh', 'headline': 'Senior UI/UX Designer-Developer at Kovai.co', 'last': 'waran', 'public_id': 'logesh-designer', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAAscQkAB_n9ZNECzSMXhqNsU4B2lWenFrPs'}], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 2, 'num_likes': 89, 'num_reposts': 2, 'posted': '2025-05-21 05:31:07', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'What does trust look like?\n\nIt’s knowing that your company will stand by its word, so you plan ahead, even before the bonus reaches you.\nIt’s when the timing feels just right, as life’s big moments align with a promise kept.\nIt’s using that bonus not just for yourself, but to give back to the community, too.\n\nThese stories from our people reflect the deeper value of our Together We Grow Bonus at Kovai.co.\n\nGayathri R | Logesh waran\n\n #TogetherWeGrow #Peoplefirst #Sharingsuccess', 'time': '3 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_togetherwegrow-peoplefirst-sharingsuccess-activity-7330827464161538049-nywt', 'urn': '7330827464161538049', 'video': {'duration': 46000, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQFqNL7gnl8Sug/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZbxUlP7GsBc-/0/1747805464405?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=N8giFMUNLJWsKZ03HVDNiPzveaELrZnPdlqfylbyUJ4'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 1, 'num_empathy': 1, 'num_interests': 1, 'num_likes': 116, 'num_praises': 1, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-05-16 11:00:10', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Swipe through the photos, but don’t stop there. \n\nHead over to our blog to read the full journey of this season’s KPL Cricket Tournament at Kovai.co! 🏏\n\nWe have captured the entire story right from the auction till the final winning moment.\n\n🔗 https://lnkd.in/gcUyyH9H\n\n#KPL2025 #cricket #CorporateGames #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '3 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_kpl-cricket-tournament-2025-activity-7329098332855762944-irBs', 'urn': '7329098332855762944'}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 2, 'num_comments': 2, 'num_empathy': 3, 'num_likes': 131, 'num_praises': 3, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-05-15 12:31:04', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': '🏆 Last Minute Legends take the win!\n\nThey defeated the Deccan Chargers by 9 runs.\n\nFrom the very first ball to the final cheer, this Saturday at Kovai.co was packed with cricket and excitement. All ten teams brought their game to the turf, and every match kept us hooked.\n\xa0\nBe it the loud cheers, the nail-biting finishes, or the final, every moment was worth the wait. 🏏\n\xa0\n#KPL2025 #cricket #CorporateGames #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '3 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_kpl2025-cricket-corporategames-activity-7328758822318014464-S_YP', 'urn': '7328758822318014464', 'video': {'duration': 50033, 'stream_url': 'https://dms.licdn.com/playlist/vid/v2/D5605AQEADUM6DzQHJQ/mp4-720p-30fp-crf28/B56ZbT7JI7GgBY-/0/1747312261705?e=1755748800&v=beta&t=KahyBAoc1B9NulgNkktLEltMHdFiygDALSk_wTV4veE'}}, {'attributes': [{'company_id': '2334263', 'name': 'Kovai.co', 'public_id': 'kovaico', 'type': 'company'}, {'first': 'Poornima', 'headline': 'Program Management | Continuous Improvement | Delivery Excellence | Agile Coaching', 'last': 'Tamizhmani', 'public_id': 'poornima-st', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAA0JsZAByWT8VlxGhftpMufAzCf6aH6kx84'}, {'first': 'Pavithra', 'headline': 'Lead Product Manager - Document360 | Driving Knowledge Management Innovation @ Kovai.co | HappyFox | Thorogood', 'last': 'Mathivanan', 'public_id': 'pavithra-mathivanan', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABew2rgBoDV_a4LUQ5R_RWiZrIzrVPKYk6A'}, {'first': 'Jubina', 'headline': 'Organic Growth Marketing Lead | B2B SaaS | Content Marketing | Search Everywhere Optimization|', 'last': 'Prabhakaran', 'public_id': 'jubinakp', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABk6BjgB1HDBxY78rn92GbV9mk4U5NDESuA'}, {'first': 'Shreeja', 'headline': 'Senior Customer Success Specialist | SaaS & KMS Expert | Onboarding & Implementation | Product Adoption | Customer Retention', 'last': 'Janarthanan', 'public_id': 'shreeja-janarthanan-a690bb95', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABQgWzEBWQVoi5OMScvA4vUttSFmvoEPb4c'}, {'first': 'Mekala', 'headline': 'Senior Lead Product Consultant | Customer Success Advocate | Speaker | Blogger | Storyteller | Product Positioning Expert | QA Specialist | Helping Companies of All Sizes Achieve Success', 'last': 'Ramesh Kumar', 'public_id': 'mekalarameshkumar', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAAPbjYIBsIO1h3eHpWcDSTyoqSc-_BtfGoE'}, {'first': 'Pradeepa', 'headline': 'Sr. Product Marketing Manager at Kovai.co', 'last': 'Somasundaram', 'public_id': 'pradeepa-somasundaram-29401255', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAAAuR8BABA2tqGC8kSTJAVQ-Oeu1AGqPaKOk'}, {'first': 'Swarna', 'headline': 'Software Test Engineer at Hewlett-Packard', 'last': 'Latha', 'public_id': 'swarna-latha-b2956579', 'type': 'profile', 'urn': 'ACoAABCiWhEBKDxzUHVGNEBqbfX5lI814h88zGU'}], 'images': [], 'num_appreciations': 1, 'num_comments': 1, 'num_empathy': 24, 'num_likes': 236, 'num_praises': 7, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-05-11 05:08:39', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'Wishing a very Happy Mother’s Day to all the incredible moms out there. 💐\n\xa0\nBehind every bedtime tale and every deadline met, there’s an untold story.\nOur working moms at Kovai.co share what it means to lead their daily life with heart and work with purpose.\n\xa0\nSwipe through to know their stories.\n\nPoornima | Pavithra | Jubina | Shreeja | Mekala | Srinithi | Pradeepa | Swarna\n\xa0\n#MothersDay #WorkingMoms #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '3 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_mothers-day-2025-activity-7327197930967236608-jDCL', 'urn': '7327197930967236608'}, {'attributes': [], 'images': [], 'num_comments': 0, 'num_empathy': 4, 'num_likes': 144, 'num_praises': 2, 'num_reposts': 0, 'posted': '2025-05-08 05:31:03', 'poster': {'linkedin_url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/kovaico/posts', 'name': 'Kovai.co'}, 'reshared': False, 'text': 'The energy is building up already!\xa0🔥 \n\nFrom rule talks and team owner meet-ups to all the action at the auction table, this year’s bidding brought a fresh new vibe.\n\nPractice sessions? Already intense.\xa0\nTeam strategies? In motion.🏏\n\nThe countdown to KPL Cricket has officially begun.\n\n🎬 Watch the pre-match moments unfold!\n\xa0\n#cricket #KPL #corporategames #TogetherWeGrow', 'time': '3 months ago', 'url': 'https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kovaico_cricket-kpl-